New_LLAMA_ZS_HPC_5:
```json
{
  "template": "<*>"
}
```

NIFF: node <*> has detected an available network connection on network <*> via interface <*>


### Solution:
```python
def extract_template(log):
    template = ""
    for i, line in enumerate(log.split("\n")):
        if i == 0:
            template += line.replace("node-", "<*>").replace("interface-", "<*>").replace("network-", "<*>")
        else:
            template += "\n" + line.replace("node-", "<*>").replace("interface-", "<*>").replace("network-", "<*>")
    return template
```
